\": \"eyJhbGciOi...\",\n  \"token_type\": \"Bearer\",\n  \"expires_in\": 3600\n}\n```\n\n## Token Expiry\n\nTokens expire after the duration specified in `expires_in`. Refresh or request a new token before expiry to avoid interruptions.\n\n## Error Responses\n\n| Status | Meaning |\n|--------|---------|\n| 401 | Missing or invalid token |\n| 403 | Token valid but insufficient permissions |\n\nSee [Errors](errors.md) for the general error format.\n", "message": "Add authentication API docs", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "path": "docs/api/authentication.md", "repo": "T16_R02_C01_A01"}, "id": "call_dd1c405cb8a7465ba9728478", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"branch": "main", "content": "site_name: Clean MkDocs Benchmark\nsite_description: Documentation benchmark repository\nnav:\n  - Home: index.md\n  - Getting Started: getting-started.md\n  - Configuration: configuration.md\n  - API:\n      - Overview: api/overview.md\n      - Authentication: api/authentication.md\n      - Errors: api/errors.md\ntheme:\n  name: material\nmarkdown_extensions:\n  - admonition\n", "message": "Add authentication page to API nav", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "path": "mkdocs.yml", "repo": "T16_R02_C01_A01", "sha": "039e25928047e875e2a9186264e36488a2a9b406"}, "id": "call_e284e1f899154df58db173b3", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8879, "output_tokens": 791, "total_tokens": 9670, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8320}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 181}}}}]}}}
